  "system": {
    "subtype": {
      "value": "skill"
    },
    "summary": {
      "value": "Double the HR of an attack but risk damaging the weapon."
    },
    "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Darkblade</strong> and <strong>Fury</strong>.</p><hr /><p>Before you perform an Accuracy Check, you may declare <strong>\"make it or break it!\"</strong>. If you do, the Check's <strong>High Roll</strong> is <strong>doubled</strong> when determining damage, but if the Result is an <strong>even</strong> number, you apply the following penalties after the attack is resolved:</p><ul><li><p>If the weapon you used is <strong>transforming</strong>, it <strong>immediately changes form</strong> and <strong>it cannot change form again</strong> until the end of the scene.</p></li><li><p>If the weapon you used <strong>is not transforming,</strong> or if it is a <strong>transforming</strong> weapon that <strong>cannot change form</strong> (see above), it is <strong>placed inside your backpack</strong> and <strong>cannot be equipped</strong> until the end of the scene; however, you may <strong>immediately</strong> perform the <strong>Equipment</strong> action <strong>for free</strong>.</p></li></ul><p>This Heroic Skill does not apply to attacks with <strong>unarmed strikes</strong>, <strong>improvised weapons</strong>, <strong>weapon modules</strong>, or <strong>Twin Shields</strong>.</p>",
